<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-13-0318 </DOCNO><TEXT>A means for locating a welding torch when welding pipework is described.An inner guide is adapted to be secured on the pipework at a predeterminedposition. It carries an outer two-part ring which carries a holder forthe torch and which is freely rotatable on the inner guide about theaxis of the pipework. A removable compartment can be provided to enclosethe apparatus and to serve as a shield for the weld zone.</TEXT></DOC>